# Sermon Files Directory

This directory stores sermon video and audio files uploaded through the Admin Dashboard.

## File Structure:
- /sermons/videos/ - Video files (.mp4, .avi, .mov, etc.)
- /sermons/audio/ - Audio files (.mp3, .wav, etc.)
- /sermons/thumbnails/ - Thumbnail images (.jpg, .png, etc.)

## Default Files:
- default.jpg - Default thumbnail for uploaded sermons
- prayer.jpg - Thumbnail for prayer-related sermons
- ramadan-prep.jpg - Thumbnail for Ramadan sermons
- family-values.jpg - Thumbnail for family-related sermons
- quran-guide.jpg - Thumbnail for Quran-related sermons
